snippet.title: Bloody Rally Show - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Bloody Rally Show is dystopian old school 2D top down roguelite racing game with infinite variety of race tracks, campaigns, missions, leaderboards, daily challenges, track editor, car editor, car tuning, customization, car battles, and multiple game modes, including one where you are a pedestrian.

Website:
https://kodolinija.com/bloody-rally-show/

Steam Page: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/926860/Bloody_Rally_Show/

Trailer Soundtrack: 
D Fast - Mr Tamone feat. en5ca
